    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "#15 Florida: Insufficient information for definite",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "conclusions, but apparently the observers on board the sailing vessel did see something",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "falling from the sky; a meteor would be very difficult, if not",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "impossible to watch, and would strike the ocean with immense impact.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "As no known aircraft were missing, and nothing was found, it is possible",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "this object was (A) a saucer landing underwater, as has been reported",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "several times in the past, (B) refuse ejected from a saucer similar to",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "the dozen or so unexplainable \"iceblocks\" that have fallen on England",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "in the last 3 years, or (C) some sort of communication signal. This",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
