      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "#17 Los Angeles, California: An ordinary report with an interesting",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "sidelight. One of the minor saucer puzzles is the connection between",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "the rather varied types of objects seen, ranging from the 1,000 foot",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "object over Godman Field, to 200 foot rocketships, to 40 foot saucers",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "to the 1 or 2 foot self-luminous globes. This is the first report I",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "have that shows a definite connection between the ordinary mysterious",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "saucers, and the very mysterious luminous small globes, whose size",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "makes its propulsion very difficult to imagine. Keyhoe has theorized",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "the saucer is a pilot-carrying ship, and the luminous small globes",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "are a non-pilot TV or radar reconnaissance device; while a writer under",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "Palmer's wing has theorized they are the actual 1 foot form of life of",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
